Server init.
>> a := Blob new: 4.
a bytes: ( List new ; Bin b00000101 ; Hx x0A ; Bin b10000001 ; 0).
>> b := Blob new: 4.
b bytes: ( List new ; Bin b00000110 ; Hx x0A ; Bin b10000000 ; 0).
# inherited blob does not get the buffer, so it's useless
# it will pass ctr_accept() but since buffer ptr == null, it will retur
>> c := a new.
{ 
>> n := a xor: c.
Out write: ['xorred:'], stop. 
Out write: n, stop. 
} except: { :e Out write: e, stop. }, start.
a free.
b free.
